The paper proposes a novel algorithm for visual question answering using a recurrent deep neural network with attention mechanism. This topic falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. The algorithm also involves optimization and training of the network, which falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-categories. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.CV and cs.CL, followed by cs.AI, cs.LG, and cs.NE.
